uint8_t const SD_CHIP_SELECT_PIN = SPI_SS_PIN

SD Chip Select pin

Warning if this pin is redefined the hardware SS pin will be enabled as an output by init(). An avr processor will not function as an SPI master unless SS is set to output mode.

For example to set SD_CHIP_SELECT_PIN to 8 for the SparkFun microSD shield: uint8_t const SD_CHIP_SELECT_PIN = 8;

The default chip select pin for the SD card is SS.
